<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="ida93aceb9-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s2200j"><num value="2200j">§ 2200j.</num><heading> Definitions</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this chapter:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="ida93aceba-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s2200j/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> The term “program” means the Defense Civilian Training Corps program established under section 2200g.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="ida93acebb-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s2200j/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> The term “member of the program” means a student at an accredited civilian educational institution who is enrolled in the program.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="ida93acebc-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/116/92/dA/tVIII/s860/a">Pub. L. 116–92, div. A, title VIII, § 860(a)</ref>, <date date="2019-12-20">Dec. 20, 2019</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/133/1514">133 Stat. 1514</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/116/283/dA/tX/s1081/a/4/A">Pub. L. 116–283, div. A, title X, § 1081(a)(4)(A)</ref>, <date date="2021-01-01">Jan. 1, 2021</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/134/3870">134 Stat. 3870</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
